"title": "5485: punishment, legal aspects of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5485: punishment, legal aspects of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The law sets out details of penalties which may be imposed upon people as a result of their committing of offences.</p>\n<h2>Just punishments</h2>\n<h3>Banishment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:23\">GEN 3:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:13-2Sam14:14\">2SA 14:13–14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:26\">EZR 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:18\">JOB 18:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:15\">JER 16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:8\">JER 23:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:14\">JER 29:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech5:3\">ZEC 5:3</a></p>\n<h3>Beating</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:2-Deut25:3\">DEU 25:2–25:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Burning</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:24\">GEN 38:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:14\">LEV 20:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev21:9\">LEV 21:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:6\">DAN 3:6</a></p>\n<h3>Confiscation of property</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth8:1\">EST 8:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:8\">EZR 10:8</a></p>\n<h3>Hanging</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:29\">JOS 8:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:22-Deut21:23\">DEU 21:22–21:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:26\">JOS 10:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam31:8-1Sam31:10\">1SA 31:8–31:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:122\">2SA 4:122</a>SA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:23\">17:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:5\">MAT 27:5</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:9-2Sam21:10\">2SA 21:9–21:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:13\">GAL 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Impaling</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:11\">EZR 6:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:19-Gen40:22\">GEN 40:19–40:22</a>EST <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:23\">2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth5:14\">EST 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Stoning</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:12-Exod19:13\">EXO 19:12–19:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:29\">EXO 21:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:2\">LEV 20:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:27\">LEV 20:27</a>LEV <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:14\">24:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:16\">LEV 24:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:23\">LEV 24:23</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:36\">NUM 15:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:10\">DEU 13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:5\">DEU 17:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:21\">DEU 21:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:21\">DEU 22:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:24\">DEU 22:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:25\">JOS 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:13-1Kgs21:15\">1KI 21:13–21:15</a></p>\n<h2>Unjust punishments and persecutions</h2>\n<h3>Banishment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:2\">ACT 18:2</a></p>\n<h3>Beating</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:26\">MAT 27:26</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:15\">MRK 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:1\">JHN 19:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:5\">ISA 53:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:37\">ACT 16:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:24\">2CO 11:24</a></p>\n<h3>Beheading</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:9-Matt14:10\">MAT 14:9–14:10</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:27\">MRK 6:27</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:16\">MRK 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:2\">ACT 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:4\">REV 20:4</a></p>\n<h3>Being thrown to wild animals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:16\">DAN 6:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:32\">1CO 15:32</a></p>\n<h3>Hanging</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:30\">ACT 5:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:39\">ACT 10:39</a></p>\n<h3>Imprisonment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:18\">ACT 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:20-Gen39:22\">GEN 39:20–39:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:27\">1KI 22:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:15\">JER 37:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6\">JER 38:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:4\">ACT 12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:23\">ACT 16:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:35\">ACT 23:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:10\">ACT 26:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23\">2CO 11:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:36\">HEB 11:36</a></p>\n<h3>Stoning</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:59\">ACT 7:59</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs12:18\">1KI 12:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:18\">2CH 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:53\">LAM 3:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:35\">MAT 21:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:19\">ACT 14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:25\">2CO 11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:37\">HEB 11:37</a></p>\n<h3>Confiscation of property</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:15-1Kgs21:16\">1KI 21:15–21:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:4\">2SA 16:4</a></p>",
